{"name":"Battle Brewer","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You expand your studies to include the alchemical sciences. You become trained in Crafting and gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.is3Oz9wt11lNq62K]{Alchemical Crafting} feat.</p>\n<p>When you use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.QDW9H8XLIjuW2fE4]{Spellstrike}, you can make a ranged @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} with an alchemical bomb, as long as the target is within the second range increment of your bomb attack. You can deliver the spell even if its range is shorter than the range increment of your bomb attack. </p>\n<p>When resolving the damage from your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.QDW9H8XLIjuW2fE4]{Spellstrike} using an alchemical bomb or a poisoned weapon, combine the acid, cold, electricity, fire, poison, or sonic damages from the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} and the spell for the purposes of resistances and weaknesses.</p>\n<p><strong>Conflux Spell</strong> @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.tDss7fcga2Dt8xu3]{Poison Blade}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (7th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.CLThxp8Qf43IQ3Sb]{Extract Poison}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (11th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.bH9cH9aDByY91l1d]{Organsight}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (13th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.TUj8eugNqAvB1vVR]{Creation}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"upgrade","path":"system.skills.cra.rank","value":1},{"key":"GrantItem","allowDuplicate":false,"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.is3Oz9wt11lNq62K"}],"slug":"battle-brewer","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/alchemical-items/drugs/alcohol.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740786866,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"0ZgBBXko5AnduUhr"}
{"name":"Manifested Blade","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Magic is your weapon, and your weapon is magical.</p>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.xzHOlMQWkn1c19cA]{Manifest Blade} conflux cantrip in addition to a conflux spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Conflux Spells </strong>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.xzHOlMQWkn1c19cA]{Manifest Blade}, @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.iXBjMI1lavEcbiYF]{Empowered Manifestation}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (7th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.kMffb6SvhCBMMI4k]{Elemental Zone}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (11th) </strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.CIjj9CU5ekeq1oLT]{Warding Aggression}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (13th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.8M03UxGXjYyDFAoy]{Weapon Storm}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"manifested-blade","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/force-fang.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740763941,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"3R3Xi85ZWvlEb5wi"}
{"name":"Combat Alchemy","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You quickly create a simple alchemical item from scraps of material supplemented with latent magic. You create one of your combat alchemical items (see below) without having to spend the normal monetary cost in alchemical reagents or needing to attempt a Crafting check. The item lasts until the start of your next turn, when it is destroyed. If this alchemical item requires a saving throw, it uses your spell DC instead of its usual DC.</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>When you first take this feat, choose two 1st- level alchemical items from your formula book as your combat alchemical items.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"combat-alchemy","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"traits":{"value":["magus","manipulate"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"battle brewer hybrid study"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685453463374,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"9KftNk6Z7u692YJr"}
{"name":"Arcane Brewing","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>When you enter @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.09iL38CZZEa0q0Mt]{Arcane Cascade} stance, you can @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.pvQ5rY2zrtPI614F]{Interact} to draw an alchemical item. While in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.09iL38CZZEa0q0Mt]{Arcane Cascade} stance, you apply the additional damage to your alchemical bombs and poisons, and the alchemical bombs you throw have a range increment of 30 feet instead of the usual 20 feet.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-effects.VffH4gFV8iZaT6bC]{Effect: Arcane Brewing}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"arcane-brewing","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"battle brewer hybrid study"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740707051,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"Qc7UNrw6kLqHUdmw"}
{"name":"Quick Manifestation","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You have two free hands.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You cast @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.xzHOlMQWkn1c19cA]{Manifest Blade} twice in rapid succession.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"quick-manifestation","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":10},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"manifested blade hybrid study"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740715336,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"TxDAqsjCcqNfKyzc"}
{"name":"Favored Manifestation","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You specialize in a type of manifested blade. Choose acid, cold, electricity, fire, or sonic. While you are in Arcane Cascade stance and wielding a @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.xzHOlMQWkn1c19cA]{Manifested Blade} of this energy type, increase the manifested blade’s damage dice to 1d8, and replace the deadly d8 trait with deadly d10 in @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.iXBjMI1lavEcbiYF]{Empowered Manifestation}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"favored-manifestation","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740712610,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"WniR90JAXpd1NMXQ"}
{"name":"Tactical Tinker","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Your studies of magic grant you insight into the use of talismans. When you use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.QDW9H8XLIjuW2fE4]{Spellstrike} and cast a spell that deals damage, your spell deals 1 additional damage if you have a talisman affixed to your armor, and 1 additional damage if the weapon you used in your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.QDW9H8XLIjuW2fE4]{Spellstrike} has a talisman affixed.</p>\n<p><strong>Conflux Spell</strong> @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.frontiers-of-the-arcane-spells.TPUq4MRANE3qlJsM]{Recall Talisman}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (7th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.q5qmNn144ZJGxnvJ]{Befitting Attire}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (11th) </strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.AMEu5zzLN7uCX645]{Ghostly Weapon}</p>\n<p><strong>Studious Spell (13th)</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.TUj8eugNqAvB1vVR]{Creation}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"tactical-tinker","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":["magus"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/precise-discipline.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685740748627,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"f1QQ7i8kfMdDaA1I"}
{"name":"Consume Talisman","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You are in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.09iL38CZZEa0q0Mt]{Arcane Cascade} stance and have a talisman affixed to your armor or weapon.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You harness the raw power of your talisman, bypassing its usual use. You destroy a talisman affixed to your armor or weapon, then make a melee @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}. Increase the additional damage from Arcane Cascade for this Strike by 1 (or by 2 if the talisman was 10th level or higher).</p>\n<p>This counts as activating the talisman for your recall talisman focus spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"consume-talisman","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"tactical tinker hybrid study"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685453461463,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"hRtvcZp7LZ7YicUU"}
{"name":"Combat Tinkering","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You quickly create a simple talisman from scraps of material supplemented with latent magic. You create one of your combat talismans (see below) without having to spend the normal monetary cost in materials or needing to attempt a Crafting check, then @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.UAaQk93a30nx0nYY]{Affix} it to your armor or weapon. The item lasts until the end of your next turn, when it is destroyed. If this talisman requires a saving throw, it uses your spell DC instead of its usual DC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> When you first take this feat, choose two common 1st- or 2nd-level talismans as your combat talismans.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"combat-tinkering","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":10},"traits":{"value":["magus","manipulate"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"tactical tinker hybrid study"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4DgChmvuIGpj5wDh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685406030273,"modifiedTime":1685453461462,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"yDcwMEWHzhp6lNP8"}
